{"tid":1338274,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"(和理非) 今日天氣咁好 今晚sing hallelujah!","createTime":"2019-07-21T12:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:33:46.000Z","uid":279962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"79b6ef7dab780414684dce8aa453a8e345113288","tid":1338274,"uid":279962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"諗諗下 出面有咩事發生<br />\n和理非族今晚都可以sing hallelujah to the lord喎!<br />\n<br />\n因為即係咁 尋日撐x就落狗屎 今日一滴雨都冇<br />\n(講真 我都唔知代表乜)<br />\n要感謝天父，好天氣讓今日活動順利進行 <br />\n<br />\n可能可以喺維多利亞公園(遊行起點, 有象徵意義)進行聖詩敬拜聚會<br />\n對出啱啱大厦寫住&ldquo;耶穌是主&rdquo;，摩頓台有播道會同福堂，可以sing足一晚hallelujah! <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人一齊唱？有冇教會弟兄姊妹出嚟講下野咁？<br />\n<br />\n守護香港 守護各區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed92c9b0fbc3b37d50186af730577d7dde17ad61","tid":1338274,"uid":279962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"遮打花園有！"},{"pid":"19c8cb1c85525e2209d7c45bba0fa5eb4d3e6bae","tid":1338274,"uid":279962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed92c9b0fbc3b37d50186af730577d7dde17ad61","tid":1338274,"uid":279962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"遮打花園有！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"大家有需要有興趣記住去！"},{"pid":"50421539b60d5812c08c314e19a66d9c2f94ba41","tid":1338274,"uid":273733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2294e0c814ca56423530e07f8b8411f30413c1c5","tid":1338274,"uid":279962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}